    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-vv40-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The Test Conditions factor achieved Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; however, the assessment team determined this gap is acceptable given that the single ASTM F1717 condition is the clinically relevant loading scenario and the model risk level 3 acceptance threshold is otherwise satisfied across all QoIs. The validation evidence supports acceptance of the FEA framework for the stated COU.",
